ic_block_settings_inset_radius\":\"field_678151576eeba\",\"generic_block_settings_z_index\":\"\",\"_generic_block_settings_z_index\":\"field_67815214d0d47\",\"generic_block_settings_background_colour\":\"floral-white\",\"_generic_block_settings_background_colour\":\"field_678154e848c16\",\"generic_block_settings_outer_background_colour\":\"white\",\"_generic_block_settings_outer_background_colour\":\"field_67c71c01a6bbc\",\"generic_block_settings_hide_panel\":\"0\",\"_generic_block_settings_hide_panel\":\"field_6793cbf801400\",\"generic_block_settings_custom_class\":\"\",\"_generic_block_settings_custom_class\":\"field_67cb16d884493\",\"generic_block_settings\":\"\",\"_generic_block_settings\":\"field_66aa4c703662f\"},\"mode\":\"edit\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/simple-text-panel {\"name\":\"acf/simple-text-panel\",\"data\":{\"content\":\"\\u003ch2\\u003eSustainable fabrication\\u003c/h2\\u003e\\r\\n\\u003cp class=\\u0022introduction\\u0022\\u003eOur unique low-temperature fabrication and short cycle times eliminate the energy-intensive processes of standard semiconductor manufacturing, helping to drive down the carbon impact of your products.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\r\\n\\u003cp class=\\u0022mb-77\\u0022\\u003eWe also use renewable energy, while optimising our processes to minimise waste generation and maximise recycling and reuse – with a special focus on the reduction of organic solvents.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003ch3\\u003eLess energy\\u003c/h3\\u003e\\r\\nLow temperatures and fewer process steps drive down energy consumption.\\r\\n\\u003ch3\\u003eLess water\\u003c/h3\\u003e\\r\\nLower temperatures mean less cooling and less ultra-pure water.\\r\\n\\u003ch3\\u003eFewer harmful chemicals\\u003c/h3\\u003e\\r\\nReducing environmental impact.\",\"_content\":\"field_6728b080153d7\",\"generic_block_settings_top_padding\":\"default\",\"_generic_block_settings_top_padding\":\"field_66aa4c8736630\",\"generic_block_settings_bottom_padding\":\"default\",\"_generic_block_settings