y-standard EDA tools?\",\"_faq_items_2_faq_title\":\"field_678d5a1625974\",\"faq_items_2_faq_content\":\"Yes, Cadence and Siemens.\",\"_faq_items_2_faq_content\":\"field_678d5a2525975\",\"faq_items_3_faq_title\":\"How thin are FlexICs?\",\"_faq_items_3_faq_title\":\"field_678d5a1625974\",\"faq_items_3_faq_content\":\"Around 37 microns, including wafer-level packaging.\",\"_faq_items_3_faq_content\":\"field_678d5a2525975\",\"faq_items_4_faq_title\":\"How flexible are they?\",\"_faq_items_4_faq_title\":\"field_678d5a1625974\",\"faq_items_4_faq_content\":\"They have a minimum bend radius of just 5mm.\",\"_faq_items_4_faq_content\":\"field_678d5a2525975\",\"faq_items_5_faq_title\":\"How are they made?\",\"_faq_items_5_faq_title\":\"field_678d5a1625974\",\"faq_items_5_faq_content\":\"Using proven, conventional semiconductor processing equipment and techniques such as photolithography on 300mm wafer carriers. The substrate preparation differs from silicon semiconductor fabrication and the number of process steps is significantly lower.\",\"_faq_items_5_faq_content\":\"field_678d5a2525975\",\"faq_items\":6,\"_faq_items\":\"field_678d59e925973\",\"generic_block_settings_top_padding\":\"default\",\"_generic_block_settings_top_padding\":\"field_66aa4c8736630\",\"generic_block_settings_bottom_padding\":\"default\",\"_generic_block_settings_bottom_padding\":\"field_66aa4cb836631\",\"generic_block_settings_move_panel_up\":\"no\",\"_generic_block_settings_move_panel_up\":\"field_67167c6560b8f\",\"generic_block_settings_inset_panel\":\"yes\",\"_generic_block_settings_inset_panel\":\"field_678151396eeb9\",\"generic_block_settings_inset_radius\":\"default\",\"_generic_block_settings_inset_radius\":\"field_678151576eeba\",\"generic_block_settings_z_index\":\"\",\"_generic_block_settings_z_index\":\"field_67815214d0d47\",\"generic_block_settings_background_colour\":\"floral-white\",\"_generic_block_settings_background_colour\":\"field_678154e848c16\",\"generic_block_settings_outer_bac