,\"slides_1_slide_description\":\"相容於支援 NFC 的行動裝置以及工業級和企業 NFC 讀取器。\",\"_slides_1_slide_description\":\"field_67a5d5fdfd4ed\",\"slides_2_slide_title\":\"13.56 MHz 工作頻率\",\"_slides_2_slide_title\":\"field_67a5d5f1fd4ec\",\"slides_2_slide_description\":\"平衡範圍、速度和功率效率—非常適合安全的短距離通訊。\",\"_slides_2_slide_description\":\"field_67a5d5fdfd4ed\",\"slides_3_slide_title\":\"26.48 kbps 資料傳輸速率\",\"_slides_3_slide_title\":\"field_67a5d5f1fd4ec\",\"slides_3_slide_description\":\"在速度和功率效率之間提供完美的平衡。\",\"_slides_3_slide_description\":\"field_67a5d5fdfd4ed\",\"slides_4_slide_title\":\"可選單面天線\",\"_slides_4_slide_title\":\"field_67a5d5f1fd4ec\",\"slides_4_slide_description\":\"降低鑲嵌物成本並減少應用厚度。\",\"_slides_4_slide_description\":\"field_67a5d5fdfd4ed\",\"slides_5_slide_title\":\"96位元組用戶內存\",\"_slides_5_slide_title\":\"field_67a5d5f1fd4ec\",\"slides_5_slide_description\":\"為廣泛的 NFC 應用提供多功能性和選擇。\",\"_slides_5_slide_description\":\"field_67a5d5fdfd4ed\",\"slides\":6,\"_slides\":\"field_67a5d489fd4eb\",\"generic_block_settings_top_padding\":\"default\",\"_generic_block_settings_top_padding\":\"field_66aa4c8736630\",\"generic_block_settings_bottom_padding\":\"default\",\"_generic_block_settings_bottom_padding\":\"field_66aa4cb836631\",\"generic_block_settings_move_panel_up\":\"no\",\"_generic_block_settings_move_panel_up\":\"field_67167c6560b8f\",\"generic_block_settings_inset_panel\":\"no\",\"_generic_block_settings_inset_panel\":\"field_678151396eeb9\",\"generic_block_settings_inset_radius\":\"none\",\"_generic_block_settings_inset_radius\":\"field_678151576eeba\",\"generic_block_settings_z_index\":\"\",\"_generic_block_settings_z_index\":\"field_67815214d0d47\",\"generic_block_settings_background_colour\":\"charcoal-grey\",\"_generic_block_settings_background_colour\":\"field_678154e848c16\",\"generic_block_settings_hide_panel\":\"0\",\"_generic_block_settings_hide_panel\":\"field_6793cbf801400\",\"generic_block_settings_custom_class\":\"\",\"_generic_block_settings_custom_class\":\"field_67cb